## Architecture

Monorepo (Turborepo + pnpm workspaces):
```
compass/
├── apps/web/          — Next.js 15 App Router (student + counselor + admin UI) → Vercel
├── apps/ai-service/   — FastAPI Python (AI endpoints: synthesis, embeddings, prompts) → Railway
├── packages/db/       — Prisma ORM + schema + Supabase WASM client
├── packages/ui/       — Shared UI components
├── packages/types/    — Shared TypeScript types
├── packages/config/   — Shared tsconfig/eslint
├── turbo.json         — Turborepo task config
└── CONTRIBUTING.md    — Migration workflow docs
```

**Tech stack:** Next.js 15.5.12, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Prisma 6 (WASM), Supabase (PostgreSQL +
pgvector), Clerk (auth — student/counselor/admin roles), Upstash Redis (caching) + QStash
(background jobs), Anthropic claude-sonnet-4-6 (synthesis), Voyage AI (1024-dim embeddings),
Vercel (web hosting), Railway (AI service hosting).

**Note:** apps/mobile was removed. Next.js upgraded from 14 to 15 in this session.

